subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Leilani Mitchell scored 19 points, Taj McWilliams-Franklin had 14 points and 10 rebounds, and the Liberty (20-11) beat the first-place Indiana Fever, 78-57, extending its team record with its ninth straight win.
